%description
Time and memory efficient estimation of multinomial logit models using
maximum likelihood method. Numerical optimization performed by
Newton-Raphson method using an optimized, parallel C++ library to achieve
fast computation of Hessian matrices. Motivated by large scale multiclass
classification problems in econometrics and machine learning.

